| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2457 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f8728904-3c30-5485-abac-7c5e60a62a8c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
